%^CYAN%^BOLD%^SHAPER%^RESET%^

The shaper has a close connection with the spirit material of the Astral Plane,
known as ectoplasm. The shaper is able to mold and frame this material to build
almost anything imaginable.

%^BOLD%^Shaper Feats:%^RESET%^
 L2 : astral construct
 L11: summoners call
 L21: astral ally

%^BOLD%^Shaper Spells:%^RESET%^
 minor creation
 ectoplasm
 creation
 wall of ectoplasm
 hail of crystals
 genesis
 astral seed
 reality revision

%^BOLD%^See Also:%^RESET%^ disciplines, kineticist, nomad, seer, telepath, egoist